---

## ğŸ›  Data Preprocessing Steps

- Handled invalid zero values  
- Treated outliers using **IQR/Z-Score**  
- Reduced skew using **Log/Box-Cox Transform**  
- Scaled numerical features (StandardScaler)  
- Encoded categorical features (Ordinal & Label Encoding)

---

## ğŸ§ª Feature Engineering

| New Feature | Purpose |
|------------|---------|
| Volume = x Ã— y Ã— z | Shape-based value signal |
| Price / Carat | Normalized pricing |
| Dimension Ratio = (x+y)/(2z) | Shape proportion |
| Carat Category (Light / Medium / Heavy) | Market segmentation interpretation |

---

## ğŸ” Exploratory Data Analysis (Highlights)

- Price increases exponentially with **carat**
- Ideal cut, D-color, IF-clarity diamonds show **highest price**
- Strong correlation found between dimensions and price

